PrecisOrder (a) consenting to amendments to the NUNAVUT LAND CLAIMS AGREEMENT that delay the starting date for the Wildlife Harvest Study and allow 24 months, instead of 12, for the Nunavut Wildlife Management Board to establish the basic need levels for beluga, narwhal and walrus, and (b) designating the Minister to consent to amendments to the Contract relating to the Implementation of the Nunavut Final Agreement.

precis:
Order (a) consenting to amendments to the NUNAVUT LAND CLAIMS AGREEMENT
that delay the starting date for the Wildlife Harvest Study and allow
24 months, instead of 12, for the Nunavut Wildlife Management Board to
establish the basic need levels for beluga, narwhal and walrus, and (b)
designating the Minister to consent to amendments to the Contract relating
to the Implementation of the Nunavut Final Agreement.
